import React from "react";

export const PorcoRossoComendoSVG = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      width="950"
      height="532"
      viewBox="0 0 712 399"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
    >
      <rect width="665" height="372" rx="40" fill="url(#pattern0)" />
      <defs>
        <pattern
          id="pattern0"
          patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox"
          width="1"
          height="1"
        >
          <use
            xlinkHref="#image0_1_10"
            transform="matrix(0.001 0 0 0.00178383 0 -0.0315827)"
          />
        </pattern>
        <image
          id="image0_1_10"
          width="1000"
          height="596"
          xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"
        />
      </defs>
    </svg>
  );
};
